    <p>Love for blending the visual, data and tech with the end user. I am passionate about technology and automation, with a strong background in leading teams, developing innovative solutions, and enhancing user experiences. I have successfully managed projects that streamline web component development, website migrations, implement AI capabilities, site analytics and ensure seamless user experience including A11Y. I prioritize maintaining high standards in security and documentation, implementing automated systems for efficiency, accuracy and consistency. </p>
